{"tid":1500762,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.22] 今日真係唔可以有衝突","createTime":"2019-08-24T06:33:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T06:42:01.000Z","uid":297962,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"14d3e614aafbe3c5716dea5cf301e331e81d40de","tid":1500762,"uid":297962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:33:22.000Z","msg":"尤其地鐵站，不然就會給人覺得地鐵好危險。封得好。<br />\n<br />\n之前機場和港鐵的做法我覺得真的不好。流失大量和理非支持者，也給人破壞社會感覺，少了表達訴求的味道。<br />\n<br />\n法庭，機管或港鐵都好，雖然一定會受政府壓力，但主要是服務市民，和只制定決策的政府不同。不是因為之前的事失去大眾支持。也不會這麼易站在社會運動對面。"},{"pid":"38bcfc01c1a0f7201f01a8c38733d2d3fd2506f7","tid":1500762,"uid":165425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:34:39.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"c2399e7734cb7bef93eb6763592f6726d87e740a","tid":1500762,"uid":297962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:35:29.000Z","msg":"自膠，是24號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa0f7391d9d37050db80bad83517059ed82521b2","tid":1500762,"uid":23663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n樓下唔使再覆"},{"pid":"3e14f6b465d72001e01128228dc6b622b89ff2cd","tid":1500762,"uid":189240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:38:21.000Z","msg":"你個名改得好呀"},{"pid":"b5e103a6fada9d8153d154cf605421aa2249ace7","tid":1500762,"uid":289681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:38:36.000Z","msg":"33130<br />\n7896<br />\n27558"},{"pid":"8a3ac0f3250a5c8ca4a89cd76d30aedd7dac303b","tid":1500762,"uid":227174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:39:08.000Z","msg":"平行時空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a976ce740a83b8ea1b8e785e702a441d405b7a","tid":1500762,"uid":273792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:39:51.000Z","msg":"好撚煩呀你d分化撚<br />\n番屋企食屎啦"},{"pid":"35107826137f370ddc4f200ca61ecfa26f156d9